fields.System.Title: R in Azure SQL DB - Create Model
fields.System.Description:
In this PBI we create the necessary tables for work with predictive models using the hotel scenario

As well we include the entity framework classes

fields.System.Title: R in Azure SQL DB - Data generator
fields.System.Description:
It is necessary to create a program that simulates historical data about bookings made by users in past years.

The generator will take into account factors like the season of the year, weather, if it is weekend or not, and so on to determine the level of occupation of a hotel.

fields.System.Title: R in Azure SQL DB - Create prediction model
fields.System.Description:
in order to predict the hotel occupation we have to create 2 scripts using R:

- Training model script
- Evaluation script

after that integrate everything with Azure SQL (that support R)

fields.System.Title: R in Azure SQL DB - Integrate with current DB
fields.System.Description: Integrate the data generator with the already created database. Add any changes to the created database if necessary to make it work as realistic as possible.
